metadata.name: life in the desert
metadata.description:
These camels are the most important element in the lives of desert Bedouins.After a long and tiring day, the thing that caught my attention the most was the Bedouins singing for these camels.This Bedouin, who was sitting with his camel to rest, explained the bond between them very well for me.

Dimensions: 5400× 3656-6.30 mb.
Resolution: 300 dpi
Location: Fas
Date: 28/10/2014
Edition: 1/1
